Usage: all_inputs [-help] [-clock <list_of_clocks>] [-no_clocks] [-edge_triggered  | -level_sensitive ]

-help                       # Prints out the command usage
-clock <list_of_clocks>     # Considers only input ports with input delay
                            # relative to the specified list of clocks
                            # (string, optional)
-edge_triggered             # Returns a collection of input ports with the
                            # set_input_delay -clock constraint (bool, optional)
-level_sensitive            # Returns a collection of input ports with the
                            # set_input_delay -level_sensitive constraint.
                            # (bool, optional)
-no_clocks                  # Returns primary input ports that do not have
                            # create_clock or create_generated_clock
                            # constraints (bool, optional)